<li><i>Homosexuality in Greece and Rome,</i> by Thomas K. Hubbard; U. of California Press, 2003. <a href="http://www.utexas.edu/courses/cc348hubbard/" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.utexas.edu/courses/cc348hubbard/" rel="nofollow">[6]</a> ISBN</li>
</ul>
